title: <span style="color: #000000;">**Republic**</span> <span style="color: #c10000;">**Protection**</span> <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**Act**</span>
subtitle: Another <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**Rathenau**</span> won't happen.
new-page: true
tags: event
view-if: year = 1922 and month = 6 and rathenau_dead
max-visits: 1 
priority: 1
face-image: img/portraits/wirth.jpg

= <span style="color: #000000;">**Republic**</span> <span style="color: #c10000;">**Protection**</span> <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**Act**</span>

Our government has drafted a new law to protect the constitutional republican order. It allows for the banning of organizations, restrictions on the freedom of assembly and the creation of a new state court to punish treason. To erase doubts raised by the <span style="color: [+ uspd_colour +];">**USPD**</span> chancellor <span style="color: [+ z_colour +];">Wirth</span> and justice minister <span style="color: [+ spd_colour +];">Radbruch</span> have stated that it will only target the political <span style="color: [+ dnvp_colour +];">**right**</span> emideatly sparking controversy. Also the Free State of <span style="color: #00CCFF;">Bavaria</span> voiced opposition supported by <span style="color: #000000;">Wurtt</span><span style="color: #c00025;">emberg</span> - they see local states rights endagered and complain over the law targetting the <span style="color: [+ bvp_colour +];">conservative South</span>.

- @let_it_be_the_reichsrat_than

@let_it_be_the_reichsrat_than
